                  , about eleven o'clock in the forenoon of the <rs id="t18180114-108-cd572" type="crimeDate">13th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180114-108-off571 t18180114-108-cd572"></join> (certain persons being therein), and stealing therein one gown, value 8s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18180114-108-victim820" type="victimName">
                     Joseph 
                     Walling
                  <interp inst="t18180114-108-victim820" type="surname" value="Walling"></interp>
